NAME

    Dist::Banshee - A lightweight authoring tool

VERSION

    0.001

DESCRIPTION

    Dist::Banshee is a lightweight authoring tool. It intends to be
    (largely) reproducible build, using scripts that are part of your
    repository.

SEE ALSO

      * Dist::Zilla

      A maximum-overkill extensible framework for building distributions.

      * App::ModuleBuildTiny

      An even more minimalist authoring tool. Functional but not
      extensible.

